Pod affinity and pod anti affinity benchmarking steps

1. Deploy 1 normal pod on 1 node each with unique label with the help of node selector.
2. Deploy 18 pods on one node each with same unique label using pod affinty and pod anti affinity.




Node affinity benchmarking steps

1. Deploy 1 normal pod on 1 node each with unique label with the help of node selector.
2. Deploy 18 pods on one node each with same unique label using node affinity.


Node anti affinity benchmarking steps

1. Same as above.
